data.description: Stunning Pagnini built, one owner Custom home on the RVCC Golf course. You will find ample room and privacy in this 3383sqft,  3 Bed, 3 bath single level home with split floor plan.  Interior boasts a Primary suite which offers incredible views of course and access to patio, Master bath has walk in shower, jacuzzi tub and large walk in closet. Huge laundry room, with large pet bath.   Kitchen is equipped with double ovens and ample storage and great for entertaining. large living room opens to Patio and is perfect for large gatherings, ''Man Cave'' with custom pool table and wet bar, hidden wine rack will WOW your guests. Exterior has Lagoon style pool with locally sourced blue stone features, In ground spa will soothe those tired muscles from a day of golfing. Custom water feature including waterfall and Koi pond will provide relaxing ambiance for those evenings on the porch. mature landscaping, Palm trees complete this back yard oasis. Dont let this opportunity pass you by
